{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-plugin-nprogress\"><a href=\"#gatsby-plugin-nprogress\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-plugin-nprogress</h1>\n<p>Automatically shows the <a href=\"http://ricostacruz.com/nprogress/\">nprogress</a> indicator\nwhen a page is delayed in loading (which Gatsby considers as one second after\nclicking on a link).</p>\n<h2 id=\"install\"><a href=\"#install\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save gatsby-plugin-nprogress</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-use\"><a href=\"#how-to-use\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to use</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// In your gatsby-config.js</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-plugin-nprogress`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// Setting a color is optional.</span>\n      color<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`tomato`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// Disable the loading spinner.</span>\n      showSpinner<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>In addition to <code class=\"language-text\">color</code> – a configuration option specific to\n<code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-plugin-nprogress</code> that saves some time\n<a href=\"https://github.com/rstacruz/nprogress#customization\">customizing the nprogress CSS</a>\nto match your site colors – you may pass all available\n<a href=\"https://github.com/rstacruz/nprogress#configuration\">nprogress configuration options</a>.</p>","excerpt":"gatsby-plugin-nprogress Automatically shows the  nprogress  indicator\nwhen a page is delayed in loading (which Gatsby considers as one…","timeToRead":1,"fields":{"title":"gatsby-plugin-nprogress"},"parent":{"__typename":"File","relativePath":"gatsby-plugin-nprogress/README.md"}},"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-plugin-nprogress","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"kylemathews","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/e567aa8adbd2d49cd9990ea1ed19d4eb"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-plugin-nprogress/","id":"4ca5cd63-9ce8-5aba-8e4a-d4983e1f3207"}}